### 2. Get All Documents
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/arc/documents?search=مستند&type=0&documentSource=0&from=2024-01-01&to=2024-12-31&pageSize=10&pageNumber=1
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### 3. Get Document by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/arc/documents/1
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### 4. Update Document
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/arc/documents/1
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "مستند التعاون التقني - محدث",
  "type": 0,
  "documentSource": 0,
  "description": "مستند يتعلق بمشروع التعاون التقني مع الشركة - محدث"
}

### 5. Download Document
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/arc/documents/1/download
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### 6. Delete Document
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/arc/documents/1
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### 7. Get Documents by Type
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/arc/documents?type=0
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### 8. Get Documents by Source
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/arc/documents?documentSource=0
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### 9. Search Documents
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/arc/documents?search=تقني
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### 10. Get Documents by Date Range
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/arc/documents?from=2024-01-01&to=2024-01-31
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

